            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, cut the cucumber in half lengthways, scrape out the seeds with a teaspoon and discard</p>\r\n<p><strong>Grate</strong> the cucumber into a mixing bowl and chop the dill (stalks too) finely&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the yoghurt, remaining garlic, dill, a pinch of salt and pepper and a drizzle of olive oil</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mix</strong> well and set aside for serving</p>",
